    "138214272": {
      "title": "Effect of bearing preload on machine tool spindle rigidity",
      "abstract": "Finite element analysis procedure and calculation method of rigidity on spindle unit of the machine tool were expounded,and calculation of the spindle rigidity was made.The effects of bearing stiffness to spindle performance under the conditions of different preload were discussed.The effect of increasing preload on spindle rigidity was discussed.The results show that the spindle bending rigidity is increased by 22% at maximum,while the effect to the natural frequency is not obvious,during the increasing of the bearing preload."
